item.title: Poe Dameron’s X-Wing
item.description: Got the new Poe Dameron’s Black X-Wing but when I opened it surprise! it is not black lol, so I have to give this guy a new paint job. I first turned everything apart so that It’s easier for me to paint. *Note: Take a lot of pictures or a video while doing this so that when it is time to put it all together you know how to do it.
